_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-1536x864.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094841/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map_teaser-747x420.jpg 747w\"></a></p><p>There’s plenty of tight, twisting tracks to explore in what Zwift calls the new Yumezi map. But it also hints of more to come as part of the larger, all-new Makuri Islands destination.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p>Just like Watopia before, Zwift locates their virtual worlds in sync with real locations so you can see them on social training sites/apps like Strava, with both of these on islands in the South Pacific. Watopia exists superimposed over the real Vanikoro in the Solomon Islands, while the new Makuri Islands appears to pop up on the 3x larger Nendö island.</p><p>(<em>Thankfully, Zwift CEO Eric Min gave us a bit of a sneak peek <a href=\"https://www.strava.com/activities/5323331422\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">via his Strava</a>!</em>) That suggests&nbsp;even more all-new virtual riding areas to come…</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094847/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094847/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Zwift new Japanese-inspired Makuri Islands virtual fantasy world, indoor training on Yumezi map\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094847/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map-scaled.jpg 2560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094847/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map-297x139.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/19094847/Zwift-new-Japanese-inspired-Makuri-Islands-virtual-fantasy-world_indoor-training-on-Yumezi-map-800x375.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.biker